Thanks
Landmark
+1 773 406 3199''', recipientProviders: [buildUser(), developers()], subject: 'success', to: 'paypal-team@gmail.com'}
   failure{
    emailext body: '''Hey guys
Build failed. Please resolve issues.

Thanks
Landmark
+1 773 406 3199''', recipientProviders: [buildUser(), developers()], subject: 'success', to: 'paypal-team@gmail.com'}
     }
  */   
}
